&Q000583 = Letter from Inim-Inana to Enlil-massu
@composite
#project: ucsl/etcsl
#atf: use unicode
#atf: use math
#etcsl: text-id=c.3.3.11
#key: after http://etcsl.orinst.ox.ac.uk/cgi-bin/etcsl.cgi?text=c.3.3.11&display=Crit&charenc=gcirc#

1. {m}{d}en-lil₂-mas-su u₃-na-a-dug₄
#lem: Enlilmassu[1]PN; dug[speak]
#etcsl: line-id=1

2. {m}inim-{d}inana-ke₄ na-ab-be₂-a
#lem: Iniminana[1]PN; e[speak]
#etcsl: line-id=2

3. inim na-me ma-an-ne-eš-ma lul-aš ba-hul₂-le
#lem: inim[word]; name[any]; e[speak]; lul[false]; hul[rejoice]
#etcsl: line-id=3

4. {d}lamma ud til₃-la-a kal-le lugal-šu₂
#lem: lammar[(female) tutelary deity]; ud[sun]; til[live (of a single person)]; kal[rare]; Lugalšu[1]PN
#etcsl: line-id=4

5. {m}na-<bi>-{d}en-lil₂ u₃ {d}en-lil₂-al-sag₉
#lem: Nabienlil[1]PN; u[and]; Enlilalsag[1]PN
#etcsl: line-id=5

6. um-mi-a šu igi du#-zu-ne
#lem: ummia[expert]; šu[hand]; igi[eye]; du[go]
#etcsl: line-id=6

7. {d}nin-imma₃ diŋir-zu
#lem: Ninimma[1]DN; diŋir[deity]
#etcsl: line-id=7

8. u₃ {d}nisaba nin ŋeštug₂ daŋal-la-ke₄
#lem: u[and]; Nisabak[1]DN; nin[lady]; ŋeštug[ear]; daŋal[wide]
#etcsl: line-id=8

9. ŋeštug₂ ha-ra-ab-šum₂-mu-ne
#lem: ŋeštug[ear]; šum[give]
#etcsl: line-id=9

10. niŋ₂ im-ma im-sar-re-a
#lem: niŋ[thing]; im[clay]; sar[write]
#etcsl: line-id=10

11. iri šu-bi nu-gi₄ al-me-a nu-e-zu-u₃
#lem: iri[city]; šu[hand]; gi[turn]; me[be]; zu[know]
#etcsl: line-id=11

12. min giŋ₄ kug-babbar diš tug₂ min {tug₂}bar-sig₉
#lem: min[two]; giŋ[unit of weight]; kugbabbar[silver]; diš[one]; tug[textile]; min[two]; barsig[garment]
#etcsl: line-id=12

13. lu₂-gen₆-na šu mu-ra-da₁₃-da₁₃# šu ti-ba-ab
#lem: Lugena[1]PN; šu[hand]; taka[set aside]; šu[hand]; teŋ[approach]
#etcsl: line-id=13

14. ha-la (1:da₁₃-da₁₃#:1) ama-zu šu nam-bi₂-te-en-teŋ₃
#lem: hala[inheritance share]; taka[set aside]; ama[mother]; šu[hand]; teŋ[approach]
#etcsl: line-id=14

:14v.1.1: (#note: 1 ms. has instead:#) da-da
#lem: taka[set aside]

15. a-ma-ru-kam
#lem: amaru[flood]
#etcsl: line-id=15






